**story**

Once upon a time, in a forest, there lived a monkey who resided on a berry tree, which was on the banks of a river. In the same forest,there lived a crocodile and his wife. On day the crocodile came tp the banks of the river and rested under the tree, the kindhearted monkey offered him some berries. The crocodile came back the next day for more berries, as he loved them. As days passed by, the crocodile and the monkey became good friends.